WEBVTT

01:56.840 --> 01:57.520
Mutou.

02:05.680 --> 02:06.960
Oh no.

02:07.360 --> 02:09.090
How do I piece it back together?

02:10.639 --> 02:13.200
Right, there seem to be words on the back.

02:23.280 --> 02:24.680
In the future, I

02:25.079 --> 02:25.760
wish...

02:26.760 --> 02:27.640
Wish I...

02:29.640 --> 02:30.760
Wish I what?

02:31.600 --> 02:34.000
It should be some kind of blessing.

02:35.440 --> 02:37.900
Wish I live as long as the Southern Mountain.

02:38.240 --> 02:38.880
Wish I

02:39.440 --> 02:40.900
eat a lot but never get fat.

02:41.000 --> 02:43.130
Wish I become more and more beautiful.

02:47.000 --> 02:48.000
If he finds out

02:48.079 --> 02:50.040
that the gift he carefully picked for me

02:50.040 --> 02:51.500
was ruined by me like this,

02:52.120 --> 02:53.720
he will definitely be angry.

02:57.920 --> 02:59.880
What exactly is in here?

03:04.640 --> 03:06.970
Now this secret has truly become a secret.

03:09.560 --> 03:10.240
Forget it.

03:11.200 --> 03:12.330
Since it's a secret,

03:12.760 --> 03:14.640
let it be a secret forever.

03:15.320 --> 03:16.680
I can't possibly go ask him

03:16.680 --> 03:18.160
what is written inside.

03:19.720 --> 03:21.250
Wouldn't that give me away?

03:21.800 --> 03:22.600
No way.

03:24.160 --> 03:25.360
I just won't tell him.

03:28.640 --> 03:29.560
I wonder if

03:30.280 --> 03:31.880
she has looked at the puzzle.

03:34.120 --> 03:35.180
Goodbye, Grandma.

03:35.960 --> 03:37.360
Goodbye. Take care.

03:42.800 --> 03:43.560
Grandma,

03:44.040 --> 03:45.600
where did Yuanbao go then?

03:46.560 --> 03:47.690
She didn't call you?

03:48.000 --> 03:51.000
She said she'll be studying at the library these days.

03:52.079 --> 03:53.740
I happen to be going there too.

03:54.600 --> 03:55.040
Well,

03:55.079 --> 03:56.040
Grandma, you should go back inside.

03:56.040 --> 03:56.800
Okay.

03:59.840 --> 04:02.280
Is she going with Meng Jingu?

04:30.960 --> 04:32.220
Do you know how to work?

04:32.920 --> 04:34.480
What are your big eyes for?

04:34.680 --> 04:35.960
Look at all this fog.

04:36.040 --> 04:37.880
Here, there, it's all fog.

04:38.000 --> 04:39.159
Wipe it over there.

04:39.720 --> 04:41.050
I'll wipe it right away.

04:47.760 --> 04:48.480
Why are you

04:48.480 --> 04:50.120
so clumsy?

04:50.320 --> 04:51.680
Can't you even mop the floor properly?

04:51.680 --> 04:52.840
Spilling everything everywhere.

04:52.840 --> 04:54.080
Do you like wiping?

05:45.640 --> 05:46.200
Go away!

05:46.200 --> 05:46.840
Dad!

05:48.760 --> 05:49.640
Sorry.

05:49.840 --> 05:50.880
I thought you were a bad guy.

05:50.880 --> 05:52.760
I saw a little girl walking alone at night.

05:52.760 --> 05:53.520
I'm sorry.

05:54.040 --> 05:54.800
It's okay.

05:55.080 --> 05:56.560
You are quite strong.

05:56.720 --> 05:57.920
I'm sorry.

05:58.440 --> 06:00.080
Why didn't you wait for me after school?

06:00.080 --> 06:02.120
I saw you were too busy with work.

06:02.200 --> 06:03.460
I can go back by myself.

06:04.280 --> 06:05.680
My daughter has grown up.

06:05.920 --> 06:07.760
But Dad still worries about you.

06:08.080 --> 06:09.160
Let's go home.

06:09.320 --> 06:11.160
Your mom made delicious food for you.

06:11.160 --> 06:11.800
Really?

06:11.880 --> 06:13.080
Let me guess.

06:13.360 --> 06:14.960
Ribs or braised fish?

06:15.160 --> 06:16.000
Both.

06:42.680 --> 06:44.760
My three lovely fairies.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.130
Good morning to you all.

06:46.360 --> 06:48.159
Everyone will have to work hard again today.

06:48.159 --> 06:50.480
But we still need to do our best.

06:51.280 --> 06:52.760
If you...

06:52.880 --> 06:55.159
If you are tired, we can take turns resting.

06:55.159 --> 06:56.480
You can call me anytime.

06:56.480 --> 06:58.409
I'd be happy to take turns with you.

06:59.120 --> 07:00.320
Always remember

07:00.680 --> 07:03.880
that we will always be a family.

07:04.720 --> 07:06.040
Let's do our best!

07:11.080 --> 07:13.080
What's wrong with him today?

07:13.160 --> 07:14.440
Is he crazy?

07:24.080 --> 07:25.360
Spare my life, young hero.

07:25.360 --> 07:26.600
Let's talk this out.

07:27.640 --> 07:30.040
Is being a bubble tea shop manager such a big deal?

07:30.040 --> 07:30.720
If you ever dare

07:30.720 --> 07:32.960
to boss your employees around again,

07:33.040 --> 07:34.700
I'll make sure you can't walk.

07:34.880 --> 07:37.560
If you want to play the big boss, I'll leave you bedridden.

07:37.560 --> 07:39.240
I-I'll never do it again.

07:39.280 --> 07:40.200
Never again.

07:41.240 --> 07:42.200
It hurts.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.400
Shang Ningyu.

08:36.120 --> 08:36.840
Yuanbao,

08:36.880 --> 08:38.200
Auntie, where is Mutou?

08:38.200 --> 08:39.559
Weren't you two going to attend

08:39.559 --> 08:41.080
your classmate's birthday?

08:41.080 --> 08:42.409
Yes. Did he leave first?

08:43.159 --> 08:45.160
This kid. Why didn't he wait for you?

08:45.560 --> 08:47.200
It's fine. I'll go by myself.

08:48.440 --> 08:50.400
Then be safe on the road, Yuanbao.

08:50.840 --> 08:51.720
Okay.

08:52.480 --> 08:53.320
This kid.

08:55.480 --> 08:56.040
Bro,

08:56.560 --> 08:58.760
you're doing this to let Yuanbao relax.

08:59.120 --> 09:01.120
But you're making me bleed out.

09:03.320 --> 09:07.160
I might not even have enough for food.

09:07.760 --> 09:08.620
How much short?

09:09.880 --> 09:11.080
Three hundred.

09:23.400 --> 09:24.730
Don't tell anyone else.

09:24.920 --> 09:25.760
Don't worry, bro.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.400
My mouth is like a safe,

09:27.480 --> 09:28.200
so tight

09:28.600 --> 09:30.130
it doesn't even let air out.

09:32.160 --> 09:33.720
Doesn't let air out, huh?

09:34.600 --> 09:35.560
My mom fed me

09:35.560 --> 09:37.490
a lot of sweet potatoes last night.

09:38.400 --> 09:39.200
Sorry, bro.

09:47.160 --> 09:48.280
Hubby, here.

09:50.040 --> 09:51.760
Jingu, are you going out?

09:52.520 --> 09:53.780
I have something to do.

09:57.600 --> 09:58.400
Good morning.

09:58.800 --> 10:00.080
Good morning, Uncle and Aunt.

10:00.080 --> 10:01.520
Xinrui, come in.

10:02.400 --> 10:03.800
Xinrui, why

10:04.200 --> 10:05.160
are you here?

10:05.840 --> 10:08.160
Didn't I tell you I was going out today?

10:08.560 --> 10:10.440
I was bored staying home alone.

10:10.800 --> 10:12.860
Where are you going? Take me with you.

10:14.200 --> 10:16.000
It's not very convenient for me.

10:16.320 --> 10:18.780
You used to take me with you when you went out.

10:19.000 --> 10:20.560
Just let me go with you.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.080
Exactly.

10:23.400 --> 10:24.600
Xinrui just came back.

10:24.600 --> 10:26.000
You should take her out more.

10:26.000 --> 10:27.320
I'm not going out for fun.

10:27.320 --> 10:28.520
I really have something to do.

10:28.520 --> 10:31.040
What important things could a student like you have to do?

10:31.040 --> 10:32.280
No matter where you go today,

10:32.280 --> 10:33.560
you must take Xinrui with you.

10:33.560 --> 10:34.560
Otherwise, you can't go either.

10:34.560 --> 10:35.280
You guys...

10:41.880 --> 10:43.560
Jingu, just listen to me.

10:43.960 --> 10:46.820
Don't you still want to buy that medical insurance?

10:49.960 --> 10:52.000
Please, take me with you.

10:52.320 --> 10:52.960
I promise.

10:53.520 --> 10:54.440
I won't bother you.

10:54.440 --> 10:56.080
I'll just stay quiet, okay?

10:56.960 --> 10:57.600
Son.

10:59.880 --> 11:01.960
Come on, eat and drink whatever you want.

11:01.960 --> 11:02.720
Today,

11:03.720 --> 11:04.520
it's my treat.

11:05.440 --> 11:07.240
Come on, brother. Let me toast you first.

11:07.240 --> 11:09.680
It's been eight cans, serve some food.

11:09.800 --> 11:11.000
I'm so full.

11:11.040 --> 11:12.680
Let's drink first.

11:12.880 --> 11:14.520
I can't swallow it anymore.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.040
Have another drink. Have another drink.

11:16.040 --> 11:17.080
When will the hot dishes be served?

11:17.080 --> 11:18.680
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

11:18.920 --> 11:19.780
Still waiting?

11:21.880 --> 11:23.440
What time is it now?

11:23.800 --> 11:24.640
Wait a little longer.

11:24.640 --> 11:26.570
I really can't swallow it anymore.

11:30.280 --> 11:31.440
Yuanbao, over here.

11:34.120 --> 11:35.580
Everyone is here so early.

11:35.840 --> 11:37.760
We're all waiting for you. Hurry up.

11:37.760 --> 11:39.090
Yuanbao, come sit here.

11:39.800 --> 11:40.360
Move over.

11:40.360 --> 11:41.890
We've been waiting for you.

11:43.080 --> 11:45.480
Then let's start.

11:46.640 --> 11:47.160
Come on.

11:47.800 --> 11:49.260
I'm lighting the candles.

11:51.280 --> 11:57.760
Happy birthday to you.

11:58.120 --> 12:01.360
Happy birthday to you.

12:01.720 --> 12:04.960
Happy birthday to you.

12:05.200 --> 12:07.040
Happy birthday.

12:09.600 --> 12:10.800
Thank you, everyone.

12:11.080 --> 12:13.280
It's so great to have you all here.

12:14.360 --> 12:16.160
Happy birthday to my little brother.

12:16.160 --> 12:18.420
May you get beaten less by Mom from now on.

12:18.480 --> 12:19.960
Bro, what are you saying?

12:20.600 --> 12:24.000
Shang Ningyu, I wish all your dreams come true.

12:24.120 --> 12:25.920
That's a great wish from Ruirui.

12:27.120 --> 12:29.040
I wish you speak with eloquence

12:29.120 --> 12:30.650
and stop talking nonsense.

12:31.480 --> 12:32.560
Xiong Yuanbao,

12:32.640 --> 12:34.640
I found that you have learned bad things now.

12:34.640 --> 12:35.720
It's my turn.

12:36.640 --> 12:37.900
I wish you, my brother,

12:38.080 --> 12:39.560
a very happy birthday,

12:39.680 --> 12:41.600
never to return,

12:41.640 --> 12:42.720
and gone.

12:42.720 --> 12:43.120
Once you go,

12:43.120 --> 12:44.600
it's all over.

12:44.720 --> 12:45.320
Alright.

12:45.360 --> 12:46.640
Smooth sailing!

12:48.480 --> 12:49.280
Shang Ningyu,

12:49.320 --> 12:51.380
wish you good health and all the best.

12:51.480 --> 12:52.560
Thank you, class monitor.

12:52.560 --> 12:53.560
Success in your studies!

12:53.560 --> 12:54.160
Thank you.

12:54.600 --> 12:57.040
You guys have said almost all the good words,

12:57.040 --> 12:58.370
and left nothing for me.

12:59.200 --> 13:00.440
Then, I wish...

13:00.480 --> 13:01.280
Got it.

13:02.480 --> 13:03.240
Got it, bro.

13:03.280 --> 13:05.280
Longevity and good fortune, right?

13:05.600 --> 13:06.240
I get you.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.000
Shang Ningyu,

13:09.280 --> 13:10.320
happy birthday.

13:11.520 --> 13:14.440
I hope all of us good friends

13:14.520 --> 13:16.640
can always be by your side.

13:17.320 --> 13:18.450
Thank you, Qiao Yan.

13:18.480 --> 13:20.240
It's great that you could come.

13:20.600 --> 13:21.400
Thanks.

13:23.200 --> 13:24.720
Is everyone here?

13:24.760 --> 13:25.820
Let's cut the cake.

13:26.000 --> 13:26.760
Time to cut the cake.

13:26.760 --> 13:28.960
Cut the cake. Cut the cake. Cut the cake.

13:29.440 --> 13:31.080
Didn't you invite someone else?

13:31.080 --> 13:31.760
Who?

13:32.400 --> 13:33.440
Right, right, right.

13:33.440 --> 13:34.640
I invited Meng Jingu.

13:34.720 --> 13:36.040
Look at my memory.

13:36.120 --> 13:37.840
I even forgot the person I invited.

13:37.840 --> 13:39.840
Let's wait a little longer.

13:43.040 --> 13:44.880
Cheers, cheers, cheers.

13:47.760 --> 13:48.320
Jingu.

13:48.360 --> 13:49.290
Happy birthday.

13:49.480 --> 13:50.480
Hello, everyone.

13:54.760 --> 13:55.880
Xinrui is here too.

13:56.160 --> 13:56.760
Well,

13:57.600 --> 13:58.800
have a seat.

14:00.240 --> 14:00.800
Sit down.

14:03.880 --> 14:04.360
Xinrui,

14:04.440 --> 14:05.800
come and sit here.

14:05.880 --> 14:07.200
Sit here.

14:07.320 --> 14:07.920
Okay.

14:11.240 --> 14:12.920
Happy birthday, Shang Ningyu.

14:12.920 --> 14:15.520
I heard from Jingu that it's your birthday today.

14:15.520 --> 14:17.280
But I didn't know what you liked.

14:17.280 --> 14:17.680
No need.

14:17.680 --> 14:18.680
So I brought this,

14:18.800 --> 14:20.560
an album signed by Jay Chou.

14:20.600 --> 14:21.330
It's for you.

14:23.960 --> 14:25.320
This...

14:25.360 --> 14:29.600
It's really an album signed by Jay Chou.

14:30.000 --> 14:30.800
Yeah.

14:31.920 --> 14:34.400
My uncle's friend organizes concerts,

14:34.440 --> 14:36.170
and got it specifically for me.

14:36.480 --> 14:37.160
Bro.

14:37.480 --> 14:40.840
I figured this birthday of yours is totally worth it.

14:41.200 --> 14:42.560
You hit the jackpot.

14:43.200 --> 14:45.080
Xinrui, you are too kind.

14:45.560 --> 14:46.800
Well, I know.

14:47.760 --> 14:48.680
I just got here,

14:48.800 --> 14:50.800
so we might not be very familiar yet.

14:51.480 --> 14:53.480
Before I came, I was afraid

14:53.480 --> 14:55.140
I would spoil everyone's fun.

14:55.400 --> 14:56.960
I hope you don't mind.

14:57.400 --> 14:58.640
Not at all.

14:58.720 --> 14:59.760
Why would we mind?

14:59.800 --> 15:00.600
Of course not.

15:01.760 --> 15:02.560
That's great.

15:03.200 --> 15:05.560
Yuanbao, you don't mind either, do you?

15:08.480 --> 15:09.880
Why would I mind?

15:10.520 --> 15:11.850
I'm glad you could come.

15:12.400 --> 15:13.600
I was actually afraid

15:13.640 --> 15:15.560
you would misunderstand me

15:15.760 --> 15:17.640
because of the notebook incident.

15:17.640 --> 15:19.440
I wouldn't. It's in the past.

15:21.600 --> 15:22.200
By the way.

15:22.760 --> 15:25.040
I know you all like Jay Chou,

15:25.240 --> 15:27.880
so I got a few extras for you guys.

15:27.920 --> 15:28.240
Thank you.

15:28.240 --> 15:29.280
I hope you like them.

15:29.280 --> 15:31.680
Thank you. I don't like Jay Chou's songs.

15:33.720 --> 15:34.440
I like them.

15:36.440 --> 15:37.040
Thank you.

15:37.560 --> 15:38.760
This is for you.

15:39.480 --> 15:40.880
I don't like them either.

15:42.120 --> 15:44.050
Bro, you like them. Did you forget?

15:44.520 --> 15:45.320
Take it away.

15:49.160 --> 15:49.960
Ruirui.

15:59.880 --> 16:00.520
Yuanbao.

16:01.120 --> 16:01.760
Thank you.

16:03.000 --> 16:04.160
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

16:04.160 --> 16:06.160
I gave it to Jingu's family already.

16:08.120 --> 16:08.840
I know.

16:10.000 --> 16:12.260
You all probably don't know me very well.

16:12.320 --> 16:13.840
Actually, I don't have many friends.

16:13.840 --> 16:15.360
Jingu is my only friend.

16:15.720 --> 16:17.320
That's why he brought me here today.

16:17.320 --> 16:18.960
I just joined this class,

16:19.280 --> 16:21.480
and I really want to fit in with everyone.

16:21.480 --> 16:23.200
But I didn't know what you all like,

16:23.200 --> 16:25.280
so I brought these.

16:25.880 --> 16:26.540
From now on,

16:26.680 --> 16:28.560
just tell me what you like from now on.

16:28.560 --> 16:30.760
I'll share whatever I have with you all.

16:32.040 --> 16:33.320
I used to think

16:33.400 --> 16:35.960
pretty girls like you would be hard to approach.

16:35.960 --> 16:38.480
I didn't expect you to have such a great personality.

16:38.480 --> 16:39.560
What do you call this?

16:39.560 --> 16:43.290
This is truly beauty and brains, like a lotus rising from the water.

16:43.560 --> 16:45.320
Gentle and lovely.

16:45.440 --> 16:47.120
No, you flatter me.

16:47.200 --> 16:48.200
I'm not that good.

16:48.320 --> 16:49.760
Actually, I think

16:50.360 --> 16:52.480
the most outstanding girl in your class

16:52.480 --> 16:53.400
is Yuan Bao.

16:55.600 --> 16:57.760
To be liked by so many classmates,

16:57.800 --> 16:59.660
she must have something special.

17:00.160 --> 17:02.840
Yuan Bao, please take care of me in the future.

17:06.560 --> 17:08.040
I was worried before I came.

17:08.040 --> 17:10.119
I didn't expect everyone to be so nice.

17:10.119 --> 17:11.440
Why would you be worried?

17:11.440 --> 17:13.240
Everyone welcomes you, right?

17:13.400 --> 17:14.000
Yes.

17:14.079 --> 17:15.740
We should also thank Gu Xinrui

17:15.760 --> 17:17.000
for the gifts she brought us.

17:17.000 --> 17:19.400
Let's applaud and welcome Gu Xinrui.

17:19.640 --> 17:22.000
Welcome, warm welcome.

17:22.040 --> 17:22.880
Thank you.

17:22.920 --> 17:24.480
Welcome, warm welcome.

17:24.520 --> 17:26.040
You guys are so nice, really.

17:26.040 --> 17:27.160
Thank you.

17:27.640 --> 17:28.800
Really, thank you.

17:32.520 --> 17:33.720
Are you done talking?

17:34.320 --> 17:36.800
Sorry, I might have talked too much.

17:38.280 --> 17:40.480
You, come downstairs with me to order.

17:48.680 --> 17:51.040
Actually, it's just right.

18:03.640 --> 18:05.240
Meng Jingu, what do you mean?

18:05.560 --> 18:06.800
You knew perfectly well that before the summer vacation,

18:06.800 --> 18:07.880
everyone was unhappy

18:07.880 --> 18:09.120
because of the notebook incident.

18:09.120 --> 18:10.850
Yet you brought Gu Xinrui here.

18:10.880 --> 18:12.800
Are you intentionally making things difficult for Yuanbao?

18:12.800 --> 18:15.160
I had no choice but to bring Xinrui along.

18:16.560 --> 18:17.400
No choice?

18:17.880 --> 18:20.040
What, did she threaten you with her life?

18:20.040 --> 18:21.900
I can't explain it to you clearly.

18:21.960 --> 18:22.640
Anyway,

18:23.160 --> 18:24.490
it's not what you think.

18:24.880 --> 18:25.560
Also,

18:25.960 --> 18:27.760
I genuinely came to celebrate Shang Ningyu's birthday

18:27.760 --> 18:29.040
and make everyone happy.

18:29.040 --> 18:31.170
I didn't know Xinrui would say so much.

18:31.720 --> 18:32.680
You didn't know?

18:33.280 --> 18:34.960
Gu Xinrui kept saying

18:34.960 --> 18:36.560
that you wanted to bring her.

18:36.880 --> 18:38.720
You saw the atmosphere just now.

18:39.360 --> 18:41.480
A perfectly good classmate's birthday party

18:41.480 --> 18:43.640
turned into a welcome party for Gu Xinrui.

18:43.640 --> 18:44.520
What is this?

18:45.120 --> 18:46.720
Where does that leave Yuanbao?

18:46.720 --> 18:48.720
I don't want to argue with you today.

18:48.720 --> 18:50.320
I'll clean up the mess I made.

18:50.440 --> 18:52.440
I have nothing more to explain to you.

18:52.440 --> 18:53.770
I'm going to order food.

18:59.760 --> 19:00.920
Autographed?

19:01.040 --> 19:02.000
What are you doing?

19:02.000 --> 19:02.640
Yuanbao.

19:03.360 --> 19:04.160
A toast to you.

19:04.480 --> 19:05.880
If you consider me a friend,

19:05.880 --> 19:06.800
drink this.

19:08.760 --> 19:09.880
If you don't drink,

19:10.160 --> 19:11.520
I'll assume you're still mad at me

19:11.520 --> 19:13.640
over the notebook from the other day,

19:14.120 --> 19:15.520
and I'll be heartbroken.

19:20.920 --> 19:22.200
We can't drink alcohol.

19:22.200 --> 19:23.460
Let's just have water.

19:24.240 --> 19:25.320
You are not kids anymore.

19:25.320 --> 19:27.320
It's just a glass of beer. It's fine.

19:30.800 --> 19:32.960
I have really never drunk alcohol before.

19:32.960 --> 19:35.040
How about we just have soft drinks?

19:36.400 --> 19:36.840
Come on.

19:36.840 --> 19:38.040
Xinrui. Xinrui. Xinrui.

19:38.040 --> 19:39.320
We can't drink alcohol.

19:39.320 --> 19:41.040
Although she usually acts like a tomboy,

19:41.040 --> 19:42.960
she probably hasn't even seen alcohol.

19:42.960 --> 19:44.040
I offered you a toast on purpose

19:44.040 --> 19:45.600
to clear up the misunderstanding.

19:45.600 --> 19:48.080
It's too disrespectful if you don't drink it.

19:48.080 --> 19:49.360
Gu Xinrui, that's enough.

19:49.360 --> 19:50.920
It's meaningless to keep acting up.

19:50.920 --> 19:52.400
No, what did I do?

19:52.480 --> 19:53.940
I just offered her a toast.

19:54.000 --> 19:57.120
Why make it sound like I'm deliberately making things difficult for her?

19:57.120 --> 19:57.780
Aren't you?

19:58.520 --> 19:59.160
Okay.

20:00.600 --> 20:01.960
Soda is fine, right?

20:04.200 --> 20:06.530
Deep feelings, let's see who drinks more.

20:07.640 --> 20:08.440
I'll go first.

20:18.320 --> 20:18.850
Yuanbao.

20:31.120 --> 20:31.880
All right.

20:35.640 --> 20:36.200
Xinrui.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.240
Bei.

20:41.080 --> 20:41.760
Yuanbao, you...

20:41.760 --> 20:42.800
Stop drinking, you two.

20:42.800 --> 20:43.960
That's enough, Xinrui.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.160
That's enough.

20:45.680 --> 20:46.540
That's enough.

20:50.360 --> 20:51.220
That's enough.

20:56.520 --> 20:57.920
Deskmate.

20:58.080 --> 20:58.840
Jingu.

21:08.760 --> 21:09.400
Yuanbao.

21:10.200 --> 21:10.920
I'm sorry.

21:11.960 --> 21:12.960
I'm sorry, guys.

21:14.240 --> 21:16.280
I'll make it up to you next time.

21:17.000 --> 21:17.930
I'm leaving now.

21:19.480 --> 21:20.400
Jingu.

21:20.840 --> 21:21.480
Jingu.

21:21.760 --> 21:22.820
Wait for me, Jingu.

21:39.480 --> 21:41.160
Jingu, what's wrong

21:41.600 --> 21:42.440
with you?

21:43.600 --> 21:44.600
What do you think?

21:44.840 --> 21:46.160
What's wrong with you today?

21:46.160 --> 21:47.920
Why did you keep picking on Yuanbao?

21:47.920 --> 21:49.250
I wasn't picking on her.

21:49.800 --> 21:51.760
I brought her a gift and offered her a toast.

21:51.760 --> 21:53.620
Why do you say I was picking on her?

21:55.880 --> 21:56.440
Jingu.

21:57.240 --> 21:57.960
Jingu.

21:59.200 --> 22:00.930
You said she's just a deskmate.

22:02.000 --> 22:02.960
Are you sure?

22:06.040 --> 22:07.440
No matter what you think,

22:07.840 --> 22:08.600
Xinrui,

22:09.200 --> 22:11.280
I want to tell you clearly today.

22:12.400 --> 22:13.920
We are grown up now.

22:14.560 --> 22:16.420
We can't be like when we were kids.

22:17.480 --> 22:19.200
I have my own life and friends.

22:19.320 --> 22:20.720
Please don't interfere.

22:21.120 --> 22:21.880
Also,

22:22.680 --> 22:24.140
we are brother and sister.

22:28.840 --> 22:29.600
Why?

22:30.920 --> 22:31.880
Why?

23:15.480 --> 23:16.200
Yuanbao.

23:16.880 --> 23:19.240
I had a terrible attitude before,

23:19.320 --> 23:21.160
so please forgive me.

23:21.600 --> 23:23.760
You are a smart

23:24.040 --> 23:25.080
and capable girl.

23:25.720 --> 23:27.650
Although you were clumsy at first,

23:27.840 --> 23:29.680
you quickly got the hang of it.

23:30.280 --> 23:31.120
Here,

23:31.880 --> 23:34.040
I wish you success in your studies

23:34.480 --> 23:35.610
and a bright future.

23:37.040 --> 23:39.160
This milk tea is still very sweet.

23:39.720 --> 23:40.920
But this summer vacation

23:40.920 --> 23:43.360
is full of strange flavors.

23:44.040 --> 23:46.680
I was busy taking extra classes, picking up bottles,

23:46.680 --> 23:48.610
and interning at the milk tea shop.

23:48.760 --> 23:50.520
For some reason, Mutou

23:50.560 --> 23:52.290
suddenly rarely came to see me.

23:52.760 --> 23:54.360
Maybe I was too busy.

23:55.360 --> 23:56.520
I managed to find some free time

23:56.520 --> 23:59.160
and finished watching the TV drama 'Struggle'.

23:59.160 --> 24:01.360
The secret behind Meng Jingu's puzzle

24:01.600 --> 24:03.200
remains a secret.

24:03.320 --> 24:05.040
At Shang Ningyu's birthday party,

24:05.040 --> 24:06.770
Gu Xinrui's sudden appearance

24:06.840 --> 24:08.640
made me feel extra uneasy

24:08.800 --> 24:10.130
about the new semester.

24:14.480 --> 24:15.040
Yuanbao.

24:16.400 --> 24:18.130
The puzzle I gave you last time,

24:19.240 --> 24:20.240
did you finish it?

24:22.600 --> 24:24.680
Puzzle.

24:25.320 --> 24:25.960
Yes.

24:26.240 --> 24:28.680
Oh no. He still remembers it.

24:29.000 --> 24:30.000
What should I say?

24:31.440 --> 24:32.000
Yuanbao.

24:34.160 --> 24:35.160
I finished it.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.160
I finished it.

24:36.360 --> 24:37.000
Then,

24:37.560 --> 24:38.760
the words on the back,

24:39.440 --> 24:40.370
you saw them too?

24:40.440 --> 24:42.960
If I tell him I ruined the puzzle

24:43.240 --> 24:44.280
and couldn't figure out

24:44.280 --> 24:45.960
what the secret behind it is,

24:46.640 --> 24:47.800
will he get angry?

24:50.360 --> 24:51.420
Are you willing to?

24:53.360 --> 24:54.360
Here's the thing.

24:54.880 --> 24:56.120
I think,

24:56.200 --> 24:57.530
since it's your secret,

24:58.760 --> 25:00.360
we better keep it low-key.

25:02.560 --> 25:03.360
Don't worry,

25:03.480 --> 25:05.880
I will definitely keep this secret for you.

25:06.000 --> 25:07.080
My lips are sealed.

25:10.560 --> 25:12.040
What is it? A leaf again?

25:12.360 --> 25:12.840
No.

25:13.080 --> 25:13.880
Let's go back.

25:17.040 --> 25:19.200
What's wrong with Meng Jingu today?

25:19.320 --> 25:20.720
He's looking at me weirdly,

25:20.720 --> 25:22.240
and what he said is strange too.

25:22.240 --> 25:22.770
Yuanbao.

25:24.040 --> 25:24.640
Okay.

25:34.520 --> 25:35.720
What happened to you?

25:35.960 --> 25:37.880
I fell during the city training.

25:40.920 --> 25:42.200
How did you end up like this?

25:42.200 --> 25:42.920
Don't ask.

25:44.480 --> 25:45.240
Mu Qingjun.

25:45.880 --> 25:47.960
Don't let sitting together affect your studies.

25:47.960 --> 25:48.960
Don't worry, sir.

25:55.400 --> 25:56.480
I have an announcement to make.

25:56.480 --> 25:59.000
The autumn sports meet is coming up soon.

25:59.320 --> 26:00.920
Every sophomore class in the school...

26:00.920 --> 26:03.240
we will hold a men's basketball tournament

26:03.240 --> 26:05.320
to help everyone integrate into the class better.

26:05.320 --> 26:06.520
The rules are simple.

26:06.640 --> 26:07.960
The science classes will compete first.

26:07.960 --> 26:10.440
The winner

26:10.640 --> 26:12.080
will play the winner of the humanities classes in the finals.

26:12.080 --> 26:13.440
Some of you might think

26:13.760 --> 26:15.960
it's a waste of time and delays your studies.

26:15.960 --> 26:16.880
But Zhicheng

26:16.960 --> 26:18.220
has always emphasized

26:18.400 --> 26:20.800
comprehensive development in morality, intelligence, physical fitness, aesthetics, and labor.

26:20.800 --> 26:22.480
We will never let you just study all the time.

26:22.480 --> 26:25.140
So, you need to balance your studies and health.

26:25.160 --> 26:25.960
Teacher,

26:26.600 --> 26:27.920
what about us girls?

26:28.440 --> 26:29.700
The girls in each class

26:29.760 --> 26:31.680
need to prepare a cheerleading squad.

26:31.680 --> 26:33.440
Even though cheerleaders don't compete,

26:33.440 --> 26:35.240
I still hope you can do a good job.

26:35.640 --> 26:36.880
Given that some students in our class

26:36.880 --> 26:38.140
in your freshman year,

26:38.400 --> 26:40.600
had experience in the drama competition

26:40.600 --> 26:43.640
I'd like Meng Jingu

26:43.840 --> 26:46.040
and Xing Yaqi to be in charge of this activity.

26:46.040 --> 26:46.920
Do you two have any problems with that?

26:46.920 --> 26:47.720
No problem.

26:47.880 --> 26:49.080
No problem, Mr. Tian.

26:49.800 --> 26:51.200
As for the class monitor,

26:51.240 --> 26:53.360
I'll leave it to Xing Yaqi.

26:53.480 --> 26:54.720
Does anyone have any objections?

26:54.720 --> 26:56.200
No.

26:56.360 --> 26:57.000
Good.

26:57.400 --> 26:59.000
Then we'll have self-study for this class.

26:59.000 --> 27:01.480
Xing Yaqi, organize the class.

27:01.520 --> 27:02.380
Okay, Mr. Tian.

27:06.280 --> 27:07.080
Oh my god.

27:07.160 --> 27:08.400
I didn't expect that in our sophomore year,

27:08.400 --> 27:09.240
our homeroom teacher

27:09.240 --> 27:10.800
would still be Mr. Tian Yong.

27:10.800 --> 27:12.520
And our chemistry teacher is still Da Meili.

27:12.520 --> 27:14.120
What kind of fate is this?

27:14.160 --> 27:15.360
And I heard

27:15.480 --> 27:16.640
that Big Rooster He Qing,

27:16.640 --> 27:17.720
Ms. Xu, and Mr. Zhong

27:17.720 --> 27:18.840
all followed us to sophomore year.

27:18.840 --> 27:19.640
Really?

27:24.600 --> 27:25.730
Don't you love ribs?

27:25.920 --> 27:27.380
I got two portions for you.

27:27.480 --> 27:28.160
Eat.

27:28.800 --> 27:29.860
If it's not enough,

27:30.400 --> 27:31.200
I'll get more.

27:32.400 --> 27:33.200
It's enough.

27:33.360 --> 27:34.480
Thank you.

27:36.040 --> 27:37.370
What are your plans now?

27:37.560 --> 27:38.280
It's fine.

27:38.360 --> 27:40.720
I'll rest for a year and try again next year.

27:40.720 --> 27:41.920
You're so energetic.

27:42.280 --> 27:42.920
Of course.

27:44.360 --> 27:46.560
Any progress with Grandpa and Grandma?

27:47.280 --> 27:50.340
Yuanbao is unwilling, so what progress could there be?

27:50.440 --> 27:51.880
What about you two?

27:53.080 --> 27:54.880
Someone suddenly got in the way.

27:56.480 --> 27:58.210
If it's really good for Yuanbao

27:58.320 --> 28:00.560
and helps her future studies,

28:01.720 --> 28:02.760
I'll back off.

28:03.560 --> 28:05.800
That doesn't sound like the Mu Qingjun I know.

28:05.800 --> 28:07.160
How can you give up?

28:14.560 --> 28:15.720
Miaomiao, did you hear?

28:15.720 --> 28:17.080
Shui transferred schools.

28:17.080 --> 28:18.200
Which Shui?

28:18.560 --> 28:19.440
You know,

28:19.520 --> 28:21.160
the former top guy at Yuhong.

28:21.200 --> 28:23.400
He transferred to Peiying for his senior year.

28:23.400 --> 28:25.040
Is it that Shui

28:25.120 --> 28:27.320
who had a grudge against Mu Qingjun because of Xiong Yuanbao?

28:27.320 --> 28:28.280
Yes, that's him.

28:28.360 --> 28:30.000
I heard that after he transferred schools,

28:30.000 --> 28:31.320
he seemed to have dropped out

28:31.320 --> 28:32.980
and fights outside every day.

28:33.560 --> 28:35.360
Such boys are so annoying.

28:35.480 --> 28:37.680
I think boys should be clean and fair,

28:37.720 --> 28:38.760
love to study,

28:38.880 --> 28:40.200
just like Meng Jingu.

28:41.080 --> 28:42.200
Speaking of Meng Jingu,

28:42.200 --> 28:43.600
I saw him

28:43.640 --> 28:45.320
eating with Xiong Yuanbao in the cafeteria a while ago,

28:45.320 --> 28:47.080
and he kept putting food in her bowl.

28:47.080 --> 28:48.480
Why do boys with good grades

28:48.480 --> 28:50.120
always hang out with girls

28:50.160 --> 28:51.640
who have average grades?

28:52.600 --> 28:54.120
Chang Yu, when do you think

28:54.120 --> 28:56.480
a top student will put food in my bowl?

28:57.640 --> 28:59.400
You'd better study hard.

28:59.880 --> 29:00.480
Let's go.

29:21.840 --> 29:24.520
Are you really quitting the cheerleading performance?

29:24.520 --> 29:27.360
I have no choice. I have to take a vocal grading test.

29:27.360 --> 29:28.920
There's a schedule conflict.

29:28.920 --> 29:31.180
Then who will be the captain if you leave?

29:31.960 --> 29:32.960
Well,

29:33.960 --> 29:36.360
Mr. Tian will probably arrange something.

29:42.640 --> 29:45.120
Summer has quietly passed, leaving behind a little secret.

29:45.120 --> 29:47.040
Today, a kid from Class Seven

29:47.280 --> 29:49.520
passed out after running two laps in PE class.

29:49.520 --> 29:50.400
The doctor said

29:50.400 --> 29:52.200
it's hypoglycemia and a lack of exercise.

29:52.200 --> 29:53.520
Kids these days

29:53.560 --> 29:55.280
really have poor physical fitness.

29:55.280 --> 29:55.960
Exactly.

29:56.040 --> 29:56.440
Let me tell you,

29:56.440 --> 29:58.040
this tradition at our school is really great.

29:58.040 --> 29:59.360
Once kids reach their sophomore year,

29:59.360 --> 30:00.480
the academic pressure is immense.

30:00.480 --> 30:03.210
They need good health to survive these two years.

30:03.360 --> 30:05.200
That's why this basketball tournament

30:05.200 --> 30:06.920
not only builds up the kids' bodies,

30:06.920 --> 30:08.240
but also keeps their enthusiasm high.

30:08.240 --> 30:08.680
Yeah.

30:08.720 --> 30:10.240
I remember when we were in school,

30:10.240 --> 30:12.240
we paid a lot of attention to physical exercise.

30:12.240 --> 30:13.760
Now that we are working,

30:13.840 --> 30:17.240
we are busy and stressed, so we don't have time for it anymore.

30:21.640 --> 30:22.240
All right.

30:22.800 --> 30:24.160
Class, stop writing.

30:24.920 --> 30:26.650
I have an announcement to make.

30:26.840 --> 30:28.170
Class monitor Xing Yaqi

30:28.280 --> 30:29.940
has a vocal grading exam soon,

30:29.960 --> 30:31.820
so she can't join the cheer squad.

30:31.840 --> 30:32.640
I propose

30:33.040 --> 30:34.360
that the cheer captain

30:34.480 --> 30:35.960
be Gu Xinrui.

30:36.280 --> 30:37.240
Any objections?

30:38.640 --> 30:39.440
I disagree.

30:40.480 --> 30:42.120
Mu Qingyun recommended Xiong Yuanbao.
